2:T940,[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Place","name":"Lower East Side","description":"The Lower East Side is New York City at its most unfiltered — a palimpsest of immigrant history and avant-garde culture compressed into a dense grid south of Houston Street. Once the entry point for w","url":"https://withpush.co/neighborhoods/lower-east-side","geo":{"@type":"GeoCoordinates","latitude":40.7157,"longitude":-73.9863},"address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Lower East Side","addressRegion":"NY","addressCountry":"US"},"containedInPlace":{"@type":"City","name":"New York City"}},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How does Push work in Lower East Side?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Push connects local creators with merchants in Lower East Side, Manhattan. Creators visit participating businesses, scan a QR code to verify their visit, then publish content. Merchants pay only for verified foot traffic — no guessing required."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How many campaigns are active in Lower East Side right now?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Lower East Side currently has 28 active creator campaigns across 38 merchants, with 127 creators operating in this neighborhood."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the average campaign payout in Lower East Side?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The average campaign payout in Lower East Side is $42 per verified visit. Total verified visits in this neighborhood have reached 3,614."}}]},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"ItemList","name":"Featured Merchants in Lower East Side","numberOfItems":3,"itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Katz's Delicatessen","address":"205 E Houston St, New York, NY 10002","description":"Food & Drink business in Lower East Side with 1 active Push campaign."}},{"@type":"ListItem","position":2,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Attaboy","address":"134 Eldridge St, New York, NY 10002","description":"Nightlife business in Lower East Side with 2 active Push campaigns."}},{"@type":"ListItem","position":3,"item":{"@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Scarr's Pizza","address":"22 Orchard St, New York, NY 10002","description":"Food & Drink business in Lower East Side with 2 active Push campaigns."}}]}]4:T4f7,The Lower East Side is New York City at its most unfiltered — a palimpsest of immigrant history and avant-garde culture compressed into a dense grid south of Houston Street. Once the entry point for waves of Jewish, Puerto Rican, and Chinese immigrants, the LES today holds all of that layered identity alongside a thriving creative economy. Orchard Street still has fabric shops and delis next to concept bars and art galleries. Katz's Delicatessen has served pastrami since 1888 and still draws lines. Push campaigns here lean into the neighborhood's gritty authenticity — merchants don't want polished content, they want real, documentary-style coverage that reflects the neighborhood's character. The dining scene is exceptional and eclectic: Vietnamese bánh mì, traditional Jewish deli, izakaya, Mexican mezcal bars, and some of the city's most serious cocktail programs. After midnight, the LES becomes one of the city's most concentrated nightlife zones — a campaign opportunity no other neighborhood replicates at that volume. Creator activity peaks Thursday through Saturday. Verified visit data shows 60% of Push campaigns in this neighborhood are fulfilled during evening hours, making the LES uniquely suited for nightlife and dining-focused creators.0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","main",null,{"className":"nh-page","children":[["$","section",null,{"className":"nhd-hero","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container nhd-hero-inner","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"nhd-breadcrumb","aria-la